location.fullValue: McMahon Plan, Cottage Courts at Daybreak

data.description: SIGNIFICANT SELLER CONCESSION TOWARDS BUYER CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY-DOWN! Welcome to your dream home in the coveted Daybreak community with this charming single-family residence! Located among the peaceful SpringHouse 55+ neighborhood, this craftsman has a carefully designed living space and offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere and a well-thought-out floor plan. The heart of the home is the open-concept living area, connecting the living room, dining space, and a modern kitchen. The kitchen features sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. With three bedrooms, this home provides plenty of space for a growing family or hosting guests. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, complete with an en-suite bathroom, offering a private space to unwind. Additionally, there are two more bedrooms, ensuring everyone has their own comfortable space. A standout feature of this home is the 3 bathrooms, providing convenience for all occupants. The carefully designed bathrooms showcase modern fixtures and tasteful finishes, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. Enjoy the Utah sunshine and picturesque surroundings from your own backyard. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or just relaxing, the outdoor space is perfect for entertaining. The Daybreak community also offers amenities such as parks, walking trails, and community events, fostering a sense of community. The renowned HOA ensures a well-maintained community, providing a multitude of amenities and services that enhance the overall quality of life for residents.
